<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:17:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国和加拿大外长周五在北京会晤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-canadian-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-friday-2024-07-18/</link><description>渥太华周四表示，加拿大外交部长梅兰妮·乔利将于周五在北京会见中国外交部长王毅，就双边关系和安全问题进行会谈。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 15:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-canadian-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-friday-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>丹麦与其他欧盟国家一起抗议欧尔班的俄罗斯之行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/denmark-joins-other-eu-states-protest-orbans-russia-trip-2024-07-18/</link><description>丹麦外交部长周四表示，该国不会派部长参加本月与匈牙利担任欧盟轮值主席国有关的非正式政府会议，以抗议总理维克多·欧尔班与俄罗斯和中国总统的会谈。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 12:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/denmark-joins-other-eu-states-protest-orbans-russia-trip-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，诺镍公司正在洽谈在中国建设电池行业镍工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/nornickel-talks-build-china-nickel-plant-battery-sector-sources-say-2024-07-18/</link><description>三名知情人士告诉路透社，俄罗斯诺镍公司正在与几家中国电池公司进行谈判，以建立一家联合工厂，利用俄罗斯半成品生产镍材料。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 11:19:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/nornickel-talks-build-china-nickel-plant-battery-sector-sources-say-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着古巴人采用电动自行车和汽车，哈瓦那的道路发生了变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/havanas-roads-change-cubans-adopt-electric-bikes-vehicles-2024-07-18/</link><description>哈瓦那以色彩缤纷的老式汽车而闻名，至今仍可以看到它们在街道上行驶，也是游客拍照的热门主题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 11:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/havanas-roads-change-cubans-adopt-electric-bikes-vehicles-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：台积电稳定芯片，欧洲央行和Netflix关注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-18/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国重申崇高的政策目标，但未提供实施细节</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-industrial-modernisation-raft-other-reforms-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国领导人周四重申了广泛的经济政策目标，从工业现代化到扩大内需以及遏制债务和房地产行业风险，但没有详细说明实施步骤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:59:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-industrial-modernisation-raft-other-reforms-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对欧盟猪肉发起反倾销调查，点名丹麦、荷兰、西班牙企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-singles-out-danish-dutch-spanish-firms-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-pork-2024-07-18/</link><description>中国周四将丹麦皇冠公司以及荷兰和西班牙猪肉公司列为对欧盟猪肉进口进行反倾销调查的目标，北京方面加大了对欧盟限制其电动汽车出口的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-singles-out-danish-dutch-spanish-firms-anti-dumping-probe-into-eu-pork-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>政府可能购买中国战略锗价格创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/price-chinas-strategic-germanium-hits-record-high-possible-state-buying-2024-07-18/</link><description>业内消息人士称，在中国最大生产国锗的价格周三创下历史新高，而锗是芯片制造的关键战略金属，受政府可能购买的猜测推动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/price-chinas-strategic-germanium-hits-record-high-possible-state-buying-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>意大利航母战斗群参加澳大利亚军演并将访问菲律宾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-carrier-strike-group-joins-australia-war-games-will-visit-philippines-2024-07-18/</link><description>意大利海军高级官员周四表示，首次部署到印度-太平洋地区的意大利航母战斗群将在澳大利亚与美国盟友参加军演后穿过南海前往菲律宾。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-carrier-strike-group-joins-australia-war-games-will-visit-philippines-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>干邑高管和欧盟官员出席北京白兰地倾销听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cognac-executives-eu-officials-attend-beijing-hearing-brandy-dumping-2024-07-18/</link><description>法国干邑白兰地协会在一份声明中表示，法国干邑白兰地公司高管和欧盟官员周四在北京出席了有关中国对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查的听证会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cognac-executives-eu-officials-attend-beijing-hearing-brandy-dumping-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国共产党罢免最高机构中前外长、国防部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，周四，在中国共产党最大的最高决策机构会议上，中国共产党将前外交部长和国防部长秦刚和李尚福撤出中央委员会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:51:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-removes-ex-foreign-defence-ministers-top-body-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：受客户退出影响，普华永道将大幅削减中国合伙人薪酬</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hit-by-client-exits-pwc-slash-china-partners-pay-sources-say-2024-07-18/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，普华永道 (PwC) 已要求其中国合作伙伴减薪最多 50%，因为对该公司的监管调查以及部分企业客户的离开促使成本削减，裁员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 07:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hit-by-client-exits-pwc-slash-china-partners-pay-sources-say-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>台积电第二季度利润增长36% 好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q2-profit-rises-36-better-than-forecast-2024-07-18/</link><description>台湾芯片制造商台积电周四公布第二季度净利润增长 36%，超出市场预期，因人工智能应用中使用的半导体需求激增。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-q2-profit-rises-36-better-than-forecast-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：随着贸易紧张局势加剧，筹码下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-18/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:39:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市下跌后美国芯片股波动，中美争端成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</link><description>美国芯片股周四大幅抛售，此前有报道称美国正在考虑收紧对中国先进芯片技术的出口限制，导致亚洲芯片股暴跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asia-tech-stocks-skid-deepening-sino-us-chip-war-2024-07-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>